Wild symbol substitutes for all symbols.
During any spin, one or more Prize symbols may appear on the reels.
Each Prize symbol value may range from 0.5x of the total bet amount up to 500x of the total bet amount.
When 5 or more Prize symbols appear anywhere on the reels, wins from all Prize symbols will be awarded.
During any spin, the Fortune Rabbit Feature with 8 Fortune Spins may be randomly triggered while the reels are spinning.
During the Fortune Rabbit Feature, only Prize symbols will appear on the reels.
Only the highest win per bet line is paid.
Bet lines win if the winning symbols are in succession  from the leftmost reel to the right.
The maximum win amount is %{5000}x of the bet amount.
Fortune Tiger is a 3-reel, 3-row video slot featuring respins and x10 multiplier.
The Bet Size is set using the"Bet Size" selector.
The Bet Level is set using the"Bet Level"selector.
The Bet Amount is set using the "Bet Amount" selector.
"Cash Wallet" displays the cash available for wager.
"Auto Spin"automatically plays the game for a selected number of rounds.
Winning combinations and payouts are made according to the "Paytable".
A bet way win in cash is equal to the value shown in the "Paytable"  multiplied by the bet size and bet level.
Only the highest win per bet line is paid.
Bet lines win if the winning symbols are in succession from the leftmost reel to the right.
Simultaneous wins on different bet lines are added.
Wild symbol substitutes for all symbols.
During any spin, one or more Prize symbols may appear on the reels.
Each Prize symbol value may range from 0.5x of the total bet amount up to 500x of the total bet amount.
When 5 or more Prize symbols appear anywhere on the reels, wins from all Prize symbols will be awarded.
During any spin, the Fortune Rabbit Feature with 8 Fortune Spins may be randomly triggered while the reels are spinning.
During the Fortune Rabbit Feature, only Prize symbols will appear on the reels.
Tap to start spin at the current Bet Lines, Bet Size and Bet Level.
Tap the button or the game area during a spin to stop the reels.
Press the <Space> key to start spin at the current Bet Lines, Bet Size and Bet Level. (applicable to PC version only)
Press and Hold <Space> key will continue game spins until it is released. (applicable to PC version only)
Tap to stop Auto Spin. The number on the button indicates the remaining number of spins for Auto Spin.
Tap to reduce the Bet Amount.
Tap to increase the Bet Amount.
Tap to display the balance of available wallets.
Tap to display the Bet Options.
Bet Size: Scroll to select the Bet Size.
Bet Level: Scroll to select the Bet Level.
Bet Amount: Scroll to select the Bet Amount.
Max Bet: Tap to set Bet Size and Bet Level to maximum value.
Tap to display the Game History.
Auto Spin automatically plays the game for a selected number of spins.
Tap on the values to select number of Auto Spins.
Tap to enable or disable the Turbo Spin to reduce the duration of reel spins in the main game.
Tap to turn sound ON or OFF.
Shows the game rules and button functions.
Shows details of the previous games played. Scroll down to the end to load more records.
Tapto select the dates of games to be shown in History.
Tap to return to the Main Game.
The game is played with 5 bet lines (fixed), bet level of 1 to 10 and bet size of 0.09 to 10.00.
The maximum win amount is %{5000}x of the bet amount.
If the total win in the main game or the Fortune Rabbit Feature reaches %{5000}x of the bet amount, the spin ends.

The game will automatically return to its initial state after being idle for 90 days. Progress and status of any collection games, unfinished free games, and unfinished feature games etc will no longer be retained.
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.
In the event of disputes over game results, all game results that are shown in the game history page are absolute and final.
